::Fenox::

Fenox looks down at D and smiles. She tries to fly more carefully so 
he wouldn't get bounced around as much. At least he stopped 
struggling, but Fenox didn't transport bots too often.

"There, that's better!" She says to him, and then adds "Ya know, 
you're kinda cute."
